             <h2>What is Toggl?</h2>
              <p>
                Toggl is a time tracker built for doing more, with less.
              </p>
              <p>
                Since no business tool can (nor should) do everything, we have focused on building a timer that is easy to use, while also having powerful reporting features and openness to allow for customization and integrability.
              </p>
